                <p>Discover Rwanda's stunning landscapes, national parks, and breathtaking mountain views. From the misty volcanoes to lush rainforests, experience nature at its finest.</p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> Volcanoes National Park</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> Nyungwe Forest</li>
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> Akagera National Park</li>
                </ul>
