        </article>

        <article class="explore-feature-card">
            <div class="feature-image" style="background-image: url('/images/forest2.jpg');">
                <div class="feature-overlay"></div>
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <h3>Cultural Heritage</h3>
                <p>Experience the rich culture and traditions of Rwanda. From traditional dance to local crafts, immerse yourself in the vibrant heritage of this beautiful country.</p>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle"></i> Traditional Dance</li>
